properties.smsText: Station Update - Central
properties.speechText:
The Devonshire Street tunnel will be closed from 6pm Thursday 1 January until 5am Monday 19 January. 

Follow the detour signs for Chalmers Street or Railway Square.

You can still access and exit Central Station via Exit 1 Grand Concourse, Exit 2 Eddy Avenue, Exit 3 Elizabeth Street, Exit 5 Chalmers Street and Exit 6 Devonshire Street.

properties.smsText: Bus service changes for Central Coast
properties.speechText:
From Sunday 29 June, changes will be made to some bus services in the Central Coast region after a review to streamline bus services. These include minor timetable adjustments and extended service hoursfor a number of routes.
See the news story for more information andplan your tripfor real-time up to date information at transportnsw.info.

properties.smsText: Station Update - Central
properties.speechText:
The Devonshire Street tunnel will be closed from 6pm Thursday 1 January until 5am Monday 19 January. 

Follow the detour signs for Chalmers Street or Railway Square.

You can still access and exit Central Station via Exit 1 Grand Concourse, Exit 2 Eddy Avenue, Exit 3 Elizabeth Street, Exit 5 Chalmers Street and Exit 6 Devonshire Street.

properties.speechText:

Follow the detour signs for Chalmers Street or Railway Square.

You can still access and exit Central Station via Exit 1 Grand Concourse, Exit 2 Eddy Avenue, Exit 3 Elizabeth Street, Exit 5 Chalmers Street and Exit 6 Devonshire Street.
